Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.68,0:00:39.39,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\t(2335,2335,\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&)}命运正召唤着我们登上这盛大舞台
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.68,0:00:45.94,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}胸膛里聚光灯闪耀  脑海中思绪沸腾
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.40,0:00:53.66,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\t(5010,5010,\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&)}追梦路上  我们前赴后继洒下热泪
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.66,0:00:58.74,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使唱到心碎  仍愿相信
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.04,0:01:01.66,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}曙光就等在前方
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.66,0:01:05.12,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}你和我  共携手
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.12,0:01:08.42,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}奔赴到路尽头
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.75,0:01:12.42,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}夜空下我们也可向星辰许愿
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.42,0:01:16.18,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}向着光来的方向
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.35,0:01:21.02,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}勇敢伸出手吧  抓住那伟大的愿望
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.02,0:01:24.69,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不用管它是否是别人眼中的白日梦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.69,0:01:28.86,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}就算「最闪耀的星星将最早迎来熄灭」
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.86,0:01:32.19,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}我们也会打破这命运
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.19,0:01:35.45,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}面对无人可知的明天
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.45,0:01:39.33,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}只需听从内心的声音
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.33,0:01:42.95,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}去奔跑  去超越
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.95,0:01:44.79,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}将梦与未来
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.79,0:01:49.21,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}交织在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.46,0:01:52.80,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}用我最珍贵的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:39.39,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\t(2335,2335,\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&)}hey, 運命が呼んでいる{\fscx50} {\fscx100}for the big stage
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:45.94,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}the spotlight filling my heart{\fscx50} {\fscx100}また熱くなる想い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:53.66,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\t(5010,5010,\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&)}Ah, 夢追って淚した{\fscx50} {\fscx100}ones before me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:00:58.74,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I sing through the heartbreak{\fscx50} {\fscx100}信じたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:01.66,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}光が待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:05.12,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}I've got you You've got me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:08.42,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}最後まで進んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:12.42,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}Oh in the night we can wish on a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:16.18,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}光の先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:21.02,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}手を伸ばし続けた{\fscx50} {\fscx100}big dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:24.69,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}誰かの目には{\fscx50} {\fscx100}it's a daydream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.69,0:01:28.86,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}“All the stars that shine brightest, Burn out the fastest”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:32.19,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}ぼくら越えていける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:35.45,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誰も知らない{\fscx50} {\fscx100}tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:39.33,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}心の声だけ{\fscx50} {\fscx100}follow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:42.95,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}駆け抜けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:44.79,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur2}夢と未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:49.21,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}重なるように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:52.80,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}with my pledge
Dialogue: 3,0:22:25.66,0:22:33.33,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}曾经对着镜子拭去眼泪  追逐梦想
Dialogue: 3,0:22:33.46,0:22:36.92,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在那个地方
Dialogue: 3,0:22:38.46,0:22:45.64,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}连好好给自己一个拥抱都做不到的懊悔
Dialogue: 3,0:22:45.64,0:22:51.06,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}和自尊一同  在房间中回荡
Dialogue: 3,0:22:51.22,0:22:57.73,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}珍贵的时间渐渐被夺走
Dialogue: 3,0:22:57.73,0:23:04.86,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现今我正走在那条
Dialogue: 3,0:23:04.86,0:23:09.62,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不曾放弃追寻的理想之路上
Dialogue: 3,0:23:09.62,0:23:12.62,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}要以比那时更为充实的自己
Dialogue: 3,0:23:12.62,0:23:18.08,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}去同回忆相会
Dialogue: 3,0:23:19.13,0:23:25.47,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使身处告别之中
Dialogue: 3,0:23:25.47,0:23:32.02,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们也在不断堆砌各自的理想
Dialogue: 3,0:23:32.02,0:23:36.14,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}虽然与梦中盼望的那个日子
Dialogue: 3,0:23:36.14,0:23:42.98,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}仍然相距甚远
Dialogue: 3,0:23:42.98,0:23:46.24,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但我还是想将其留到未来
Dialogue: 3,0:23:46.24,0:23:49.45,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}为了将来的我
Dialogue: 3,0:23:49.45,0:23:52.99,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}能够由衷展露笑颜
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.66,0:22:33.33,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}鏡に向かい涙を拭き夢を追ってた
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.46,0:22:36.92,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}あの場所には
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.46,0:22:45.64,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}自分を抱きしめてあげられない悔しさ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.64,0:22:51.06,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}プライドが部屋を交差してた
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.22,0:22:57.73,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}大事な時間が奪われていく
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.73,0:23:04.86,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}諦めず探した理想の道を今
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.86,0:23:09.62,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}歩いてあの頃以上に
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.62,0:23:12.62,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}満たされた私で
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.62,0:23:18.08,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}思い出に会いにいくよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.13,0:23:25.47,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}さようならの中でも
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.47,0:23:32.02,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}それぞれ理想積み上げてたんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.02,0:23:36.14,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}夢焦がれたあの日には
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.14,0:23:42.98,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}程遠いみたいだけどまだ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:42.98,0:23:46.24,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}未来にとっておくよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:46.24,0:23:49.45,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}これからの私を
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.45,0:23:52.99,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}楽しめるように
